# The build scripts only ever run under Linux (Emscripten toolchain). Checked
# out with CRLF on Windows they fail silently — /bin/sh reads the trailing \r as
# part of the shebang and the interpreter is never found, leaving the sysroot
# stubs uncreated with no obvious error. Pin them to LF regardless of platform.
*.sh text eol=lf
Makefile text eol=lf
